       </div>
       <p>
       </p>
       <p>
        The mission of the Office of Faculty Development and Diversity within the School of
                        Social Sciences at UC Irvine is to build an equitably inclusive and supportive learning
                        and working environment that nurtures respect for diversity and facilitates excellence.
       </p>
       <p>
       </p>
